    "course_title": "EDITING AND POST-PRODUCTION FOR VIDEO AND FILM",
    "description": "Focus on the theory and practice of video editing and post-production. Gain a thorough understanding of narrative editing techniques, color correction, audio post-production and the requisite software. Discusses the art of post-production and how post-production affects narrative function in moving picture media (including films, music videos, and television).",
